OL,5, Delays to support for children with    
OL,6, special educational needs in England   
OL,7, are an "acute concern", Ofsted's chief 
OL,8, inspector has told the BBC.            
OL,10,FHalf of local authorities inspected in 
OL,11,Fthe last school year had "significant  
OL,12,Fweaknesses" in their special needs     
OL,13,Fprovision, the regulator said.         
OL,15,FOfsted's annual report also says       
OL,16,Fchildren's education post-pandemic is  
OL,17,Fbeing held back by staff shortages.    
OL,19,FThe Department for Education said it   
OL,20,Fwill set out improvement plans in 2023.
